title: THE Steve Wilkos Show 05.22.08
description:
HOPE-LESS:
 ---------

A child left behind... 12-year-old Joshua recently called Steve seeking his help in finding closure with his estranged mother, Hope. It&#039;s been nine years since he last saw Hope, and simply wants to know why she never came back for him, and continued to lie for all these years. Hope meanwhile wants Steve&#039;s help to get back in her son&#039;s life, but it may be too late, as Joshua may have given up on her for good.
